Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20gifts%20should%20always%20be%20about%20sharing%20something%20with%20a%20person%20you%20care%20about%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20gratitude%20they%20show%20in%20return.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20%26quot%3Bthank%20you%20for%20the%20toaster%26quot%3B%20note%20after%20an%20event%20like%20a%20bridal%20shower.%20The%20hosts%20already%20invited%20me%20to%20share%20their%20big%20moment%2C%20usually%20throwing%20an%20elaborate%20party%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20my%20present%20a%20%26quot%3Bthank%20you%20for%20including%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20let's%20just%20call%20it%20even.%20(Rinse%20and%20repeat%20this%20approach%20with%20any%20graduations%2C%20baby%20showers%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-big-birthday-parties-kids-small-family-party-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebirthday%20parties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20other%20big%20shindigs.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20hate%20all%20thank-you%20cards%2C%20though.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20quite%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20me%2C%20the%20ones%20that%20matter%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20you%20were%20never%20obligated%20to%20send.%20They're%20cards%20from%20my%20mentees%20at%20work%2C%20sharing%20the%20ways%20that%20they've%20grown%20thanks%20to%20my%20help.%20Or%20ones%20I've%20received%20during%20tough%20times%20that%20tell%20me%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ehow%20much%20I've%20helped%20someone%20in%20the%20past%20and%20remind%20me%20I%20have%20a%20support%20system%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey're%20the%20thank-yous%20that%20are%20unexpected%2C%20but%20never%20unwanted%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20come%20straight%20from%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4f99790-80dd-4314-a308-676da1d7