%2C%20he%20insisted%20we%20stop%20by%20whenever%20it%20would%20help%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20was%20always%20ready%20with%20a%20cup%20(or%20several).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20my%20mom%20died%2C%20my%20family%20brought%20Taj%20Palace%20a%20card%20to%20let%20them%20know%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20knew%20how%20much%20their%20kindness%20had%20meant%20to%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFive%20years%20later%2C%20the%20thank-you%20card%20from%20my%20family%20is%20still%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eprominently%20displayed%20next%20to%20the%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhenever%20I%20see%20it%2C%20it%20reminds%20me%20that%20even%20the%20smallest%20things%2C%20like%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20may%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthank%20you%26quot%3B%20really%20does%20matter%2C%20and%20sometimes%20a%20card%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20still%20hate%20most%20thank-you%20notes%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20find%20me%20writing%20the%20%26quot%3Bobligatory%26quot%3B%20sort%20anytime%20soon.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20those%20who've%20made%20a%20real%20difference%3F%20Well%2C%20those%20are%20the%20cards%20that%20I'll%20always%20want%20to%20send.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-type-thank-you-notes-worth-writing-greeting-card-writer-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755609481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887da17f748d8c055f66774%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-type-thank-you-notes-worth-writing-greeting-card-writer-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20greeting-card%20writer%2C%20I%20hate%20thank-you%20notes%20for%20weddings%20and%20gifts%20sent%20out%20of%20obligation.