.%20%26quot%3BThose%20sort%20of%20like%20egg-on-the-face%20moments%20are%20what%20most%20managers%20are%20afraid%20of%2C%20and%20they%20try%20their%20damnedest%20to%20try%20to%20prevent%20those%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20tightening%20its%20performance-review%20process%20can%20also%20be%20a%20precursor%20to%20job%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20after%20Mai%20left%20Meta%20in%202022%2C%20the%20company%20laid%20off%203%2C600%20employees%2C%20or%20about%205%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%20Many%20of%20these%20employees%20were%20labeled%20%26quot%3Blow%20performers%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20title%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-low-performance-cuts-review-cycle-politics-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrailed%20some%20of%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20their%20exit.%20Months%20after%20the%20layoffs%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternal-memo-meta-increases-employees-rated-below-expectations-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternal%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Meta%20pushed%20managers%20to%20put%20more%20employees%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bbelow%20expectations%26quot%3B%20tier.%20For%20teams%20of%20150%20or%20more%2C%20Meta%20wanted%20managers%20to%20put%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20employees%20in%20the%20bottom%20bucket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20told%20employees%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bdecided%20to%20raise%20the%20bar%20on%20performance%20management%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20out%20low-performers%26quot%3B%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20recently%20employed%20a%20new%20strategy%20to%20handle%20those%20it%20viewed%20as%20poor%20performers%2C%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-pivot-amazon-low-performers-paying-employees-to-leave-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternal%20email%20to%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20pay%20them%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E