res%20and%20Alumni%20Ventures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Austin-based%20startup%20may%20have%20the%20answer%20to%20a%20crucial%20problem%20that%20the%20AI%20industry%20is%20still%20stuck%20on%3A%20how%20to%20power%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAalo%20Atomics%20says%20the%20answer%20isn't%20the%20hulking%20nuclear%20plants%20of%20decades%20past.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20betting%20on%20mass-manufactured%20smaller%20reactors%20built%20to%20sit%20beside%20the%20data%20centers%20they'll%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pitch%20earned%20the%20company%20a%20hefty%20check.%20Aalo%20recently%20closed%20a%20%24100%20million%20Series%20B%2C%20CEO%20Matt%20Loszak%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Valor%20Equity%20Partners%20led%20the%20round%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-top-defense-tech-vc-investors-to-know%23larsen-jensen-harpoon-ventures-14%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarpoon%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falumni-ventures-vc-firm-mark-edwards-investment-strategy-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlumni%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20others%20participated%2C%20bringing%20Aalo's%20total%20funding%20to%20north%20of%20%24136%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20trajectory%20shows%20just%20how%20tightly%20AI%20and%20energy%20are%20now%20linked.%20Aalo%20CEO%20Matt%20Loszak%20said%20he%20cofounded%20the%20startup%20%26quot%3Bhand-in-hand%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20started%20the%20company%2C%20we%20had%20data%20centers%20high%20up%20on%20our%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BVery%20rapidly%2C%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20we%20have%20to%20focus%20the%20entire%20company%20around%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoszak%20and%20Yasir%20Arafat%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20founded%20Aalo%20in%202023%20to%20make%20mass-manufactured%20nuclear%20power%20plants.%20The%20company's%20main%20product%20is%20the%20Aalo%20Pod%2C%20a%20small%20modular%20reactor%20built%20to%20power%20data%20centers.%20Aalo%20says%20one%20Pod%20can%20power%20roughly%2050%2C000%20homes%2C%20or%20one%20data%20center%2C%20Loszak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNuclear%20really%20is%20the%20ultimate%20underdog%2C%26quot%3B%20Loszak%20said.%20He%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20misunderstood%20technology%20I've%20ever%20seen%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20skepticism%20of%20the%20safety%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnuclear-power-us-reliance-energy-crisis-explained-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enuclear%20power%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy%20selected%20Aalo%20to%20test%20the%20company's%20experimental%20power%20plant%20Aalo-X%2C%20which%20it%20plans%20to%20complete%20construction%20for%20in%202026%2C%20at%20Idaho%20National%20Laboratory%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20Nuclear%20Reactor%20Pilot%20Program.%20This%20program%20aims%20to%20speed%20up%20testing%20of%20advanced%20reactor%20designs%20and%20authorize%20deployment%20at%20sites%20beyond%20national%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAalo%20isn't%20the%20only%20company%20getting%20a%20boost%20from%20Washington.%20Ten%20nuclear%20companies%E2%80%94including%20Antares%20Nuclear%2C%20Radiant%20Industries%2C%20Valar%20Atomics%2C%20and%20Sam%20Altman-backed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foklo-stock-price-nuclear-power-stocks-ai-data-center-trump-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOklo%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94have%20been%20tapped%20for%20the%20DOE's%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-amazon-ai-nuclear-power-grid-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-openai-big-tech-investment-nuclear-ai-race-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20become%20interested%20in%20leveraging%20nuclear%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fuel%20AI%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243638023-7a19-4252-add7-9334cfe65dc5%5C%22%3EAalo%20plans%20to%20take%20its%20technology%20global%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAalo%20aims%20to%20eventually%20take%20its%20factory-built%20model%20global.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20Aalo%20hopes%20to%20mass-produce%20reactors%20in%20large%20facilities%20like%20its%2040%2C000%20square-foot%20Austin%20factory%2C%20ship%20them%20to%20sites%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20assemble%20them%20on%20location.%20Over%20time%2C%20Loszak%20said%2C%20the%20company%20hopes%20to%20work%20with%20a%20network%20of%20partner%20developers%20who%20would%20handle%20installation%20and%20operation%20of%20the%20Aalo%20Pods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20company%20hopes%20to%20partner%20with%20customers%20%26quot%3Bwilling%20to%20pay%20a%20premium%20because%20they%20value%20the%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Loszak%20said%2C%20namely%2C%20cloud%20giants%20with%20data%20center%20projects%20in%20the%20works.%20The%20company%20declined%20to%20disclose%20which%20hyperscalers%20it's%20working%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAalo%20also%20plans%20to%20eventually%20%26quot%3Bbring%20costs%20as%20low%20as%20possible%20to%20help%20bring%20more%20energy%20to%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Loszak%20said.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20cut%20energy%20costs%20to%20around%20three%20cents%20per%20kilowatt%20hour%2C%20though%20Aalo's%20prices%20are%20currently%20higher%20than%20this%2C%20Loszak%20said.%20Energy%20costs%20can%20vary%20greatly%20depending%20on%20location%2C%20and%20electricity%20across%20all%20sectors%20in%20the%20US%20averages%20about%2013%20cents%20per%20kilowatt%20hour%20as%20of%20May%202025%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Felectricity%2Fmonthly%2Fepm_table_grapher.php%3Ft%3Depmt_5_6_a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Energy%20Information%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAalo%20will%20use%20the%20new%20funding%20to%20double%20its%20staff%2C%20growing%20from%20about%2060%20employees%20now%20to%20120%20within%20the%20next%20year.%20It%20will%20focus%20on%20hiring%20engineers%20and%20manufacturing%20talent.%20That's%20a%20sharp%20increase%20for%20a%20startup%20that%20was%20just%20Loszak%20and%20Arafat%20less%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298f7a88c-d893-4351-8d58-60c31692925d%5C%22%3EBetting%20on%20nuclear%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELoszak's%20interest%20in%20nuclear%20power%20is%20personal.%20He%20said%20he%20developed%20asthma%20while%20growing%20up%20in%20Canada%20due%20to%20coal-plant%20smog.%20Once%20the%20country%20expanded%20nuclear%20power%2C%20though%2C%20Loszak%20said%20his%20symptoms%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLo%20and%20behold%2C%20smog%20days%20went%20to%20zero%2C%20and%20my%20asthma%20went%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Loszak%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20'my%20God%2C%20this%20technology%20is%20incredible.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Loszak%20cofounded%20Humi%2C%20an%20HR%20software%20startup%20that%20Employment%20Hero%20acquired%20for%20over%20%24100%20million%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArafat%2C%20Aalo's%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%2C%20brings%20the%20nuclear%20chops.%20He%20started%20his%20career%20at%20Westinghouse%20Electric%20Company%20and%20later%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finl.gov%2Fmarvel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMARVEL%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20advanced%20nuclear%20reactor%20at%20the%20Idaho%20National%20Laboratory.%20Arafat%20earned%20his%20Ph.D.%20in%20nuclear%20engineering%20at%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20met%20him%2C%20I%20just%20knew%20he%20was%20the%20right%20guy%20to%20partner%20with.%20We%20had%20really%20similar%20values%2C%20a%20similar%20vision%20for%20what%20nuclear%20should%20become%2C%20and%20even%20a%20similar%20sense%20of%20humor%2C%20which%20is%20important%20because%20we%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Loszak%20said%20of%20Arafat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoszak%20said%20Aalo's%20investor%2C%20Valor%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20partner%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20startup%20because%20of%20its%20relationships%20with%20big%20data%20center%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValor%20backed%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI%20in%20a%20%246%20billion%20Series%20B%20in%202024%2C%20and%20the%20investment%20firm%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20lenders%20to%20secure%20up%20to%20%2412%20billion%20for%20xAI's%20plan%20to%20buy%20a%20large%20sum%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%20for%20a%20new%20mega-sized%20data%20center%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fai%2Felon-musk-x-ai-funding-feecede1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July.%20Valor%20also%20participated%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrusoes-project-stargate-data-center-tax-break-in-abilene-texas-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECrusoe's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24600%20million%20Series%20D%20in%20late%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faalo-atomics-100-million-valor-nuclear-reactor-startup-data-center-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755604802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d960885e81483682cd91d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faalo-atomics-100-million-valor-nuclear-reactor-startup-data-center-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aalo%20Atomics%20raises%20%24100%20million%20to%20mass-produce%20nuclear%20reactors%20to%20power%20data%20centers%20amid%20the%20growing%20energy%20demand%20from%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhornstein%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Hornstein)%22%2C%