0remain%20who%20I%20am%20%E2%80%94%20the%20president%20of%20a%20country%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20full-scale%20war%2C'%26quot%3B%20Avuziak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0f53766-a6a6-49b3-b574-4649937bbdbc%5C%22%3EDress%20to%20impress%2C%20not%20to%20stand%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20arrive%20to%20sign%20a%20bilateral%20security%20agreement%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%2C%20Thursday%2C%20June%2013%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Savelletri%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4302dcfc04e97619b9cd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223045%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZelenskyy%20has%20stuck%20to%20a%20wardrobe%20of%20shirts%20and%20cargo%20pants%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAlex%20Brandon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHennessy%20said%20standing%20out%20and%20showing%20personality%20make%20sense%20in%20industries%20like%20fashion%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20the%20arts.%20However%2C%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-work-fashion-tips-stylists-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20environments%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20favor%20understated%20dressing%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20still%20look%20interesting%20and%20show%20a%20point%20of%20view%2C%20but%20it%20is%20usually%20better%20to%20stick%20to%20traditional%20dress%20conventions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVodicka%20said%20workers%20have%20to%20balance%20blending%20in%20and%20standing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDressing%20to%20blend%20in%20too%20much%20can%20make%20you%20appear%20forgettable%2C%20while%20dressing%20to%20stand%20out%20too%20much%20risks%20being%20seen%20as%20unprofessional%20or%20distracting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20a%20sweet%20spot%20is%20to%20express%20individuality%20through%20subtle%20details%20like%20a%20modern%20cut%2C%20a%20well-chosen%20accessory%2C%20or%20a%20color%20that%20suits%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b25489e-97c1-4399-8d3d-c4dfce541a1e%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20wear%20for%20important%20meetings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVodicka%20said%20that%20in%20high-stakes%20meetings%20or%20interviews%2C%20how%20you%20dress%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-stylist-wealthy-tech-finance-men-elevate-uniform-wardrobe-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epowerful%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20you%20feel%20and%20are%20perceived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommends%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bmatch%20or%20slightly%20elevate%20the%20dress%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20underdressed%20can%20leave%20you%20feeling%20self-conscious%20and%20can%20distract%20others%20from%20your%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20Vodicka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20advised%20prioritizing%20quality%20over%20quantity%20by%20investing%20in%20fewer%20high-quality%20pieces%20instead%20of%20many%20ill-fitting%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvuziak%20said%20that%20polished%20fabrics%20like%20fine%20wool%20and%20poplin%20cotton%20can%20elevate%20the%20outfit%2C%20instead%20of%20denim%2C%20knitwear%2C%20and%20cheap%20polyester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvoiding%20a%20baggy%20fit%20will%20also%20help%20an%20outfit%20look%20better%2C%20Avuziak%20said.%20That%20means%20going%20for%20structured%20bags%20over%20shapeless%20totes%2C%20blazers%20over%20cardigans%2C%20and%20pointed-toe%20kitten%20heels%20over%20ballet%20flats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20comfort%20is%20key%20if%20you%20want%20to%20look%20and%20feel%20your%20best%20and%20not%20get%20distracted%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20your%20skirt%20or%20trousers%20look%20chic%20but%20the%20fabric%20is%20itchy%20or%20the%20cut%20is%20too%20snug%2C%20let%20them%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Avuziak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHennessy%20said