0going%20back%20to%20work%20after%20agreeing%20to%20a%20deal%20that%20ends%20a%20tense%20strike%20that%20led%20to%20over%202%2C700%20flights%20being%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20negotiations%20restarted%20Monday%20night%2C%20the%20union%20announced%20early%20Tuesday%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20tentative%20agreement%20after%20mediation%20had%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20union%20worked%20through%20the%20night%2C%20from%207%20p.m.%20to%204%3A23%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Canada%20Component%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendants-push-for-extra-pay-boarding-delays-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECanadian%20Union%20of%20Public%20Employees%20(CUPE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20represents%20over%2010%2C000%20cabin%20crew%20members%20at%20the%20flag%20carrier%20and%20its%20low-cost%20subsidiary%2C%20Air%20Canada%20Rouge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20the%20airline's%20700%20daily%20flights%20have%20been%20canceled%20since%20the%20strike%20began%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20affecting%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20data%20from%20FlightAware%2C%202%2C733%20flights%20operated%20by%20the%20airline%20and%20Air%20Canada%20Rouge%20have%20been%20canceled%20since%20the%20strike%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20research%20note%2C%20analysts%20at%20Raymond%20James%20estimated%20that%20the%20strike%20would%20impact%20the%20airline's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20by%20150%20million%20to%20400%20million%20Canadian%20dollars%20(%24109%20million%20to%20%24289%20million).%20It%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20timeframe%20for%20the%20strike%20it%20based%20these%20estimates%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-air-canada-boeing-787-economy-wont-book-again-review-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20suspended%20its%20guidance%20for%20the%20third%20q