t%20the%20union%20wanted%20full%20hourly%20pay%20for%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Tuesday%20statement%2C%20Air%20Canada%20CEO%20Michael%20Rousseau%20said%20it%20may%20take%20over%20a%20week%20to%20fully%20restore%20operations%2C%20with%20crew%20and%20aircraft%20out%20of%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suspension%20of%20our%20service%20is%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20our%20customers.%20We%20deeply%20regret%20and%20apologize%20for%20the%20impact%20on%20them%20of%20this%20labour%20disruption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20priority%20now%20is%20to%20get%20them%20moving%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20Canada%20also%20said%20it%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20tentative%20agreement%20until%20the%20ratification%20process%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-canada-flight-attendants-end-strike-2-700-cancellations-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755599656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a44d99194a2d49b8aec49e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-canada-flight-attendants-end-strike-2-700-cancellations-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20Canada's%20flight%20attendants'%20union%20announced%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20tentative%20agreement%20early%20Tuesday%2C%20after%20risking%20jail%20time%20to%20strike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-canada-flight-attendants-end-strike-2-700-cancellations-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20Khan's%20alleged%20illegitimate%20son's%20social%20media%20leaked%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755599526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2F