ed%20tech%20sovereignty.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEuropean%20startups%20like%20Mistral%20are%20focusing%20on%20developing%20their%20own%20AI%20infrastructure.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20Europe's%20tech%20ecosystem%20great%20again%26quot%3B%20might%20not%20fit%20on%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20badge%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20he%20might%20unintentionally%20be%20delivering%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2C%20that's%20what%20investors%20and%20founders%20on%20the%20continent%20are%20betting%20on%20as%20the%20US%20has%20become%20more%20protectionist%20with%20its%20economic%20policies%20and%20a%20less%20reliable%20ally%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20spurred%20investors%20in%20Europe%20to%20put%20more%20capital%20into%20defense%20startups%2C%20and%20tech%20companies%20and%20politicians%20to%20embrace%20so-called%20tech%20sovereignty%20in%20areas%20like%20AI%20and%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20shift%20in%20deployment%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20Flavia%20Levi%2C%20a%20deep%20tech%20VC%20at%20Europe-based%20Join%20Capital%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20how%20money%20should%20be%20going%20into%20strengthening%20the%20critical%20technologies%20of%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20founders%20and%20investors%20also%20sense%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20into%20his%20second%20term%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-tech-trends-trump-trade-war-startups-vc-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweeping%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-big-takeaways-from-trumps-approved-big-beautiful-bill-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20unsettled%20the%20US%20tech%20sector.%20They%20have%20slashed%20funding%20for%20clean%20energy%20projects%2C%20inflated%20manufacturing%20costs%20for%20hardware%20startups%2C%20and%20complicated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-ramaswamy-trump-immigration-h1b-krugman-reich-economics-tech-talent-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisa%20requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-holder-recent-grad-canceled-travel-plans-h1b-concerns-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%20entering%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216df0102-3039-44fb-90d6-cc1ffa21e863%5C%22%3EInvestors%20are%20backing%20Europe's%20defense%20startups%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20defense%20tech%20has%20been%20a%20top%20focus%20for%20investors%20in%202025%20%E2%80%94%20but%20especially%20so%20in%20Europe.%20Last%20year%2C%20defense%20startups%20on%20the%20continent%20raised%20a%20banner%20%242.4%20billion%2C%20per%20PitchBook%20data.%20This%20year%2C%20they've%20already%20clinched%20%242.11%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20with%20notable%20raises%20coming%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Helsing%20and%20Quantum-Systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration's%20unpredictable%20relationships%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20NATO%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20further%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20European%20continent%20to%20seek%20military%20and%20economic%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alexander%20Lange%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20VC%20fund%20Inflection.%20He%20added%20that%20it's%20galvanizing%20a%20whole%20generation%20of%20founders%20to%20pursue%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%20challenges%20in%20energy%2C%20compute%20infrastructure%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20defense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20attack%20on%20Ukraine%20in%202022%20reminded%20Europe%20that%20war%20is%20a%20tangible%20reality%20on%20the%20continent%2C%20Matthew%20Wright%2C%20UK%20lead%20at%20defense%20tech%20startup%20Delian%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20accelerated%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20thinking%20that%20was%20in%20place%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20encouraged%20European%20governments%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20defense%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20US%20or%20third%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20bashing%20of%20ESG%20policies%20may%20have%20also%20indirectly%20influenced%20investors'%20approaches%20to%20European%20defense%20tech%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20defense%20tech%2C%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20VCs%20and%20sometimes%20LPs%20have%20clauses%20whereby%20they%20agree%20not%20to%20invest%20in%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Levi.%20Limited%20partners%2C%20which%20provide%20capital%20for%20VCs%2C%20have%20historically%20gravitated%20to%20companies%20that%20%26quot%3Btick%20off%20ESG%20boxes%2C%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20building%20weapons%20%E2%80%94%20but%20this%20has%20started%20to%20change%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLPs%20have%20started%20to%20change%20their%20investment%20thesis%2C%20and%20they're%20removing%20these%20clauses%20so%20VC%20funds%20have%20more%20freedom%20to%20invest%20in%20defense-related%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22625246e2-78b4-49b2-8e4f-f6a9f95f9fe3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVCs%20are%20championing%20European%20tech%20sovereignty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20isn't%20the%20only%20sector%20getting%20extra%20investor%20attention%20in%20the%20Trump%202.0%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20European%20government%20leaders%20such%20as%20France's%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20the%20UK's%20Keir%20Starmer%20have%20committed%20billions%20in%20funding%20toward%20national%20AI%20ventures%2C%20often%20around%20%26quot%3BAI%20sovereignty%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20country%20or%20region%20should%20have%20control%20over%20the%20governance%20of%20its%20AI%20technologies%20and%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%