%20markets%2C%20or%20declines%20of%20at%20least%2020%25%3F%20Sure%2C%20no%20one%20likes%20a%20significant%20market%20pullback%2C%20but%20if%20you%20stay%20invested%2C%20there's%20evidence%20that%20they%20may%20not%20be%20all%20that%20painful%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20long%2C%20drawn-out%2C%20yearslong%20ruts%20in%20the%20market%20may%20be%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Hank%20Smith%2C%20the%20director%20and%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%20at%20Haverford%20Trust%2C%20which%20manages%20and%20consults%20on%20%2415.3%20billion%20of%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Smith%20laid%20out%20the%20main%20reason%20bear%20markets%20might%20be%20more%20short-lived%20going%20forward%3A%20A%20significant%20imbalance%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20shares%20on%20the%20market%20and%20demand%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20decades%20ago%2C%20the%20number%20of%20publicly%20listed%20firms%20in%20the%20US%20was%20over%207%2C000%2C%20he%20said.%20Now%20it's%20under%204%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20number%20has%20also%20been%20shrinking%20relative%20to%20the%20US%20population.%20There%20are%20about%2013%20publicly%20listed%20companies%20per%20million%20people%20today%2C%20compared%20to%2030%20companies%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FZAAnC%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FZAAnC%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20record%20amount%20of%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20%247%20trillion%20in%20money%20market%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20stock%20buybacks%20have%