0it.%20So%2C%20when%20he%20was%20nine%2C%20and%20began%20making%20excuses%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20tired%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20playing%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20to%20weasel%20his%20way%20out%20of%20playtime%2C%20his%20parents%20suspected%20something%20was%20wrong.%20In%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20they%20watched%20their%20son%20become%20a%20shadow%20of%20his%20former%20self.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lethargy%20persisted.%20It%20grew%20into%20an%20exhaustion%20that%20impaired%20him%20from%20completing%20even%20functional%20daily%20tasks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20felt%20tired%20all%20the%20time%3B%20even%20if%20I%20ate%20well%2C%20even%20if%20I%20rested%2C%20I%20was%20tired.%20There%20came%20a%20time%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Deepa%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20his%20playing%20that%20was%20affected%3B%20whatever%20it%20was%20%E2%80%94%20it%20impacted%20his%20life.%20He%20constantly%20ran%20a%20fever%2C%20and%20his%20legs%20would%20swell.%E2%80%9D%20But%20they%20shrugged%20it%20off%20as%20something%20that%20would%20%E2%80%9Cget%20better%E2%80%9D%20until%20one%20day%20Varun%20had%20to%20be%20rushed%20to%20emergency%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saumil%20Gaur%2C%20a%20paediatric%20nephrologist%20at%20the%20Rainbow%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20recalls%20his%20first%20impression%20of%20Varun%20six%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CVarun%20was%20very%20sick%20when%20I%20met%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20was%20very%20weak%3B%20his%20bones%20were%20weak%2C%20and%20they%20were%20bending.%20His%20blood%20pressure%20was%20high%2C%20and%20he%20was%20having%20seizures%20and%20was%20almost%20in%20a%20coma.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Saumil%20and%20the%20team%20soon%20discovered%2C%20Varun%20was%20battling%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebett