chools%2C%20in%20%3Cem%3Epanchayats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20governing%20bodies)%2C%20and%20corporates.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20conducted%20these%20programmes%20in%20states%20like%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20done%20numerous%20campaigns.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20other%20half%20of%20the%20battle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20awareness%20is%20one%20facet%20of%20the%20story%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398655%2Fdr-taru-jindal-doctor-improving-bihar-healthcare-district-hospital-maternal-care%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20conducive%20to%20the%20transplants.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20(2025)%2C%20only%2013%2C476%20kidney%20transplants%20were%20performed%2C%20both%20in%20government%20and%20private%20hospitals%2C%20against%20the%20recommended%201%20lakh%20cases%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20Anand%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023%3B%20he%20believes%20that%20sports%20can%20help%20one%20discover%20their%20strength%20after%20a%20transplant%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%