0of%20anyone%20who%20registers%20with%20us%20goes%20to%20the%20government%20system.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20very%20accountable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20want%20to%20sign%20up%20to%20be%20an%20organ%20donor%2C%20I%20can%20go%20on%20the%20ORGAN%20India%20website%20and%20express%20my%20intent%20to%20donate%20my%20organs.%20Once%20I%20fill%20in%20the%20details%2C%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20system.%20Once%20you%20are%20registered%20as%20an%20organ%20donor%2C%20you%20talk%20to%20your%20family%20and%20tell%20them%20about%20your%20wish%20to%20have%20your%20organs%20donated%20in%20the%20case%20you%20are%20ever%20brain-dead.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20by%20signing%20up%20to%20become%20a%20donor%2C%20you%20are%20helping%20people%20like%20Varun%20get%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life.%20In%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20getting%20the%20transplant%20was%20like%20a%20new%20chapter%20beginning.%20I%20closed%20the%20old%20book%2C%20and%20the%20transplant%20helped%20me%20write%20a%20new%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Deepa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fhealth%2Forgan-transplants-hit-by-fund-constraints-and-infrastructural-deficiencies-report%2Farticle69724663.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfrastructure%20deficiencies%2C%20low%20funds%20affecting%20organ%20transplants%20in%20India%3A%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20S%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20published%20on%2023%20June%202025.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwtg2025.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWorld%20Transplant%20Games.%3C%2Fem%3E