0Water%20it%20and%20press%20the%20soil%20from%20above%20to%20let%20it%20settle.%20It%20takes%20roughly%20an%20hour%20to%20settle%20the%20soil%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELater%20on%2C%20build%20your%20pathways%2C%20huts%2C%20or%20other%20structures.%20Decorate%20your%20garden%20with%20colourful%20pebbles%2C%20hedges%2C%20bells%2C%20dolls%2C%20and%20other%20decorative%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20the%20tray%20using%20a%20spray%20bottle%2C%20carefully.%20You%20can%20also%20spray%20liquid%20compost%20using%20kitchen%20waste%20like%20banana%2C%20garlic%2C%20ginger%2C%20and%20onion%20peels%20to%20fertilise%20soil%20and%20prevent%20the%20plant%20from%20fungal%20attacks.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20make%20the%20compost%2C%20collect%20peels%20in%20a%20bucket%20and%20add%20some%20water%20to%20it.%20After%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20strain%20the%20contents%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20clean%20water%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A2.%20Spray%20this%20fertiliser%20on%20all%20tray%20gardens%20every%20two%20to%20three%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharda%20says%20it%20takes%20her%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20to%20decorate%20the%20tray%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20get%20bored%2C%20I%20recreate%20these%20tray%20gardens%20using%20the%20same%20plants%20and%20props.%20Just%20like%20kids%20play%20with%20their%20miniature%20dollhouses%2C%20I%20have%20my%20tray%20gardens.%20My%20friends%20say%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20my%20childhood%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Sharda%20Godara.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755268200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-1716782026.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D486350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharda%20Godara%20transformed%20her%20Faridabad%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20jungle.%20She%20started%20designing%20these%20mini%20tray%20gardens%20at%20her%20home